@reeverzax - Sorry for the delayed response. Yes, we are still planning a public announcement on June 1st, around 9am PT. Please watch https://groups.google.com/g/kubernetes-security-announce for the announcement and do not publish anything before the announcement is made. You may freely discuss the vulnerability, but we would appreciate a draft of the technical details before publishing.

